text: Middletown Township is a township in Monmouth County, New Jersey, United States. As of the 2020 United States Census, the township had a total population of 67,106. Middletown is one of the oldest sites of European settlement in New Jersey."Welcome to the Throckmorton-Lippit-Taylor Burying Ground On Penelope Lane in Middletown, New Jersey" , Atlantic Highlands Herald, Spring 2003 ==References== Category:Townships in New Jersey
title: Middletown Township, New Jersey
